OL,7,FA financial director who defrauded a
OL,8,Fbusiness out of nearly #1.9 million
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FAllan Wood, 59, from Ellesmere Port
OL,12,Fappeared at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,13,Fafter pleading guilty to four counts
OL,14,Fof fraud by abuse of position in
OL,15,Frelation to his role with Cammell
OL,16,FLaird.
OL,18,FThe allegations were first reported in
OL,19,FJanuary 2021, and an investigation
OL,20,Frevealed that Wood abused his position
OL,21,Fof trust.
