OL,7,FBetween 2007 and 2008, Wood
OL,8,Ftransferred over #1.5 million into
OL,9,Fpersonal accounts held by himself, as
OL,10,Fwell as settling personal credit card
OL,11,Fexpenses.
OL,13,FHe also authorised just over #315,000
OL,14,Fof "unauthorised corporate
OL,15,Fentertainment" using company money for
OL,16,Fhimself, friends and family.
OL,18,FThis activity resulted in a total loss
OL,19,Fto the company of #1,870,243.
