OL,7,FWood has been jailed for five years
OL,8,Fand three months.
OL,10,FDuring this time, Cammell Laird were
OL,11,Fstruggling financially and the board
OL,12,Fof directors had to inject a
OL,13,Fsignificant amount of their own money
OL,14,Fto keep the company going.
OL,16,FDetective Constable Laura Madden, the
OL,17,Fofficer in charge of the case, said:
OL,18,F"This fraud placed a business under
OL,19,Fsignificant financial pressure,
OL,20,Fcausing distress and worry to all
OL,21,Femployees.
